snippet.title: Why DC is *NOT* Banning Amber Heard for Aquaman 2
snippet.description:
Why DC is *NOT* Banning Amber Heard for Aquaman 2
Celebrity breakups are difficult to predict. While it is tough for any of us to terminate relationships, it is made even more unpleasant when the breakup is made public. Actors Johnny Depp and Amber Heard are well aware of this, since the former pair has been embroiled in a public and legal battle. And now there are reports that Heard may be sacked from her starring role in Aquaman 2 in the DC Extended Universe.
